Create quality index from object of class 'fbswicd'.

create_quality.Rd

Create quality index from object of class 'fbswicd'.

create_quality(data, ..., decimal = 2)

Arguments

data

An object of class 'fbswicd'.

...

Variables used for stratification.

decimal

Decimal digits.

Value

Data frame of class quality.

Examples

library(canregtools)
file <- system.file("extdata", "411721.xls", package = "canregtools")
data <- read_canreg(file)
#> 2200  cases were read from FB sheet.1470  cases were read from SW sheet.
fbsw <- count_canreg(data, cutage_method = "interval")
#> [1] "Processing data: 2200 FBcases."
#> [1] "Processing data: 1470 SWcases."
#> [1] "Processing POP data of year: 2016"
quality <- create_quality(fbsw, year, sex, icd_cat)
